title: No Remorse - demoHATE - EP
description:
Meet the No Remorse a new trash metal band from Rio de Janeiro, Brasil. This is their first EP released some weeks ago. Hope you enjoy the sound. 

No Remose, No Regrets.

FORMATION:

Rodrigues, Igor: Lead Vocals, Rhythm & Lead Guitars
Mamede, Erick: Drums
Pellacani, Pedro: Bass Guitar, Backing Vocals

TRACKLIST:

1- Cannibal Assault (intro)
2- Growing Hate
3- Death Clock
4- Single Bullet
5- Drunkyard
6- Souls of Hipocrisy

That's it, spread the sounds.
